@startuml LangChain_TS_Agent架构图

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title Agent 架构与执行流程

package "Agent 组件" #E8F5E9 {
    [Agent\nReAct/Plan-and-Execute] as agent
    [Tools\nTool[]] as tools
    [LLM\nChatOpenAI] as llm
    [Prompt\nReAct Prompt] as prompt
    [AgentExecutor] as executor
    [Memory\nBufferMemory] as memory
}

package "执行循环" #FFF3E0 {
    [Thought\n思考] as thought
    [Action\n行动] as action
    [Observation\n观察] as observation
    [Final Answer\n最终回答] as final
}

' 架构关系
agent --> tools : has
agent --> llm : uses
agent --> prompt : uses
agent --> memory : uses
executor --> agent : orchestrates

' 执行流程
thought --> action : decides
action --> observation : tool executes
observation --> thought : feedback loop
thought --> final : complete

note right of executor
  **执行流程:**
  1. 接收用户输入
  2. LLM 生成 Thought
  3. 解析 Action (Tool)
  4. 执行 Tool 获取 Observation
  5. 循环直到 Final Answer
end note

note left of tools
  **Tool 类型:**
  - DynamicTool (函数)
  - StructuredTool (Zod Schema)
  - TavilySearch
  - Calculator
  - Custom API
end note

@enduml